<br>
I hope she writes more. Ann Brashares, wasn't it? <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:FF9900;font-family:Gigi;font-size:large;">Amy</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://home.nc.rr.com/peculiartreasure/images/bookline.gif "/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:99FF66;font-family:Enviro;font-size:x-small;">I will not believe unproved evil of you; my lips shall not utter it;<!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->my ears shall be closed against it; I too am an erring mortal,<!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->liable to stumble, apt to come short of my most earnest efforts;<!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->your lot has been harder than mine, your temptation greater, <!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->let us help each other to stand and walk without more falling!</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#9fb7df><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/bchristlikebooklovers.showUserPublicProfile?gid=lilamazing>LilAmazing</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>ezHappy</span><br>  Posts: 45<br> <font color=#3333ff>(4/1/03 7:22 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fchristlikebookloversfrm24.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=46.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: The Sisterhood of the Traveling Pants</span><hr size=1> I am so excited!  I just read that a second one in the series is coming out this month.  (April.)  I think this may be my all time favorite book.  Who was your favorite character? <p><br>
